## Key design decisions
- Pipeline branching routes by VideoType from signal_assessment, not a separate classifier call
- STOCK_PICK/SECTOR → full stock analysis (original path)
- MACRO → macro insights + conditional stock analysis
- MARKET_REVIEW → market review summary + macro insights from review
- EXPERT_INTERVIEW → expert insights + macro insights + conditional stock analysis
- NEWS_EVENT/OTHER → macro insights + conditional stock analysis
- ExpertInsight uses heuristic regex patterns (Korean name + title patterns) — no LLM call needed
- Combined dashboard deduplicates macro insights by indicator (highest confidence wins) and stocks by ticker (highest score wins)

